      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nBuild Successful \n \nSUCCESS: http://build.whamcloud.com/job/reviews-patchless-centos5/28/ \nSUCCESS: http://build.whamcloud.com/job/reviews-centos5/296/ \nSUCCESS: http://build.whamcloud.com/job/reviews-ubuntu/133/",
