        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2011-02-24 06:15:04.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThank you, Andreas. I ran acc-sm on Toro by myself (only rhel5 clients, and few mpi related tests skipped) either, and no defect is found so far.",
